data.oai_dc:dc: CT scan data of green iguana, Iguana iguana OUVC 10445

This zip file contains DICOM images from an x-ray microcomputed tomography (µCT) scan of an injected Iguana iguana (OUVC 10445). The arteries were injected with a latex and barium solution and scanned on a GE eXplore Locus in vivo Small Animal MicroCT scanner (90µm slice thickness at 80kV and 450 µA) at the Ohio University µCT Scanning Facility.
